Loss of funding impact

Q20. What impact has this loss of funding had on your group, organization and/or movement?

The greatest impact of the reduction in funding between 2021 and 2023, as observed among the organizations that responded to the survey, is seen in the decrease in their activities, with a Percentage of 60.2%, followed by a reduction in staff. It is noteworthy that the loss of funding has not had a significant impact on the discontinuation of programs or projects.
